</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C337088DF761B120B182FED8339B42CB" pageId="20" pageNumber="541" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B925B06F761B120B182FED8339B42CB" blockId="20.[151,1437,150,393]" pageId="20" pageNumber="541">
COMMENTS: Date and place agree with the journal entries. Wahlberg camped and collected at Saulspoort and immediate environs from 
<date id="FF937DC6F761B120B0F2FEB431084227" box="[439,817,331,357]" pageId="20" pageNumber="541" value="1843-10-12" valueMax="1843-11-26" valueMin="1843-10-12">12 October to 26 November 1843</date>
. The note by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFBC26F7F761B120B283FEB437314227" author="Grant, C. H. B. &amp; Praed, C. W. M." box="[966,1288,331,357]" pageId="20" pageNumber="541" pagination="30 - 31" refId="ref28552" refString="Grant, C. H. B. &amp; Praed, C. W. M. (1949) Notes on eastern and southern African birds. (2) On Mirafra passerina Gyldenstolpe. Bulletin of the British Ornithologists' Club, 69, 30 - 31." type="journal article" year="1949">Grant &amp; Praed (1949: 30-31)</bibRefCitation>
has no effect under the present Code.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
